item.title: Why cant i get on?
item.dc:creator: @zyescape zyescape
item.description:
@zyescape wrote:

if your making your own server there should be a folder saying charecters, if you go in to charecters fold and there should be a ton of notepad documents

just delete them all and then run your compile and then log in with any name and any pass!
everyone that has been on your server will have to start again though so do what you wish =)
